{"code":200,"message":"","data":{"id":"2206","movieId":"2203","title":"BBC 谁在引导我们消费","tag":"BBC·历史·纪录片","desc":"我们为什么要买东西？谁让这个世界变得无节制消费？他们如何做到这一点？调查记者雅克·佩雷蒂审视了无节制消费潮流背后的机制，得出了答案。","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/made-us-spend.png","introduces":[{"type":1000,"text":"我们为什么要买东西？谁让这个世界变得无节制消费？他们如何做到这一点？调查记者雅克·佩雷蒂审视了无节制消费潮流背后的机制，得出了答案。","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/made-us-spend01.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"原来，使这个世界变得无节制消费的元凶，并不是人们普遍认为的广告员和市场推广员，而是这诸多因素背后那些首先改变产品然后改变我们的人们。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"纪录片表明，长久以来，制造商都梦想着在消费者大脑中植入“升级”观念，从而让无限消费成为现实。他们首先瞄准未被开发的儿童市场，学习应用向儿童销售的方法，从而增加向成年人的销售。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"但是，那头最肥的能够带来现金的奶牛却来自恐惧——通过挖掘消费者的恐惧，制造商发现了一个对健康和安全产品有巨大需求的世界。","image":""}],"videos":[{"id":"2214","title":"1、第一集","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/made-us-spend.png","playCount":"3","playNumber":1,"playNumberDesc":"第一集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d22833165\u0026cid\u003d37901869\u0026page\u003d1","videoUrl":""},{"id":"2215","title":"2、第二集","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/made-us-spend.png","playCount":"3","playNumber":2,"playNumberDesc":"第二集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d22833165\u0026cid\u003d37905650\u0026page\u003d2","videoUrl":""},{"id":"2216","title":"3、第三集","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/made-us-spend.png","playCount":"3","playNumber":3,"playNumberDesc":"第三集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d22833165\u0026cid\u003d37907697\u0026page\u003d3","videoUrl":""}]}}